folder: Greenwich Street & Jane Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Greenwich Street, north from Jane Street, showing surface conditions under the Ninth Avenue Elevated. The street car tracks are being removed by the W.P.A. Intersection in the midground is Horatio Street. Gansevoort Street is beyond.
Location personally verified 9-26-1940.
